title: [Valtina's Outfitting]
[Valtina's General Store]
description: Refined oak-paneled walls rise from a varnished dark oak floor.  Just above a woven Vornavian silk rug hangs a fused sun and moon wall-hanging, and a dark and light oak ceiling completes the picture.  A Vornavian silk-lined display case stands in the middle of the room.
